trying to dig more, came across #4640 which is exactly the same issue as I am facing. I just followed the fixes pointed out removing all occurence of X86_64 bits from the build scripts compile_ios_protobuf.sh & compile_ios_tensorflow.sh and then running build_all_ios.sh
works great on device.

body:
trying to dig more, came across #4640 which is exactly the same issue as I am facing. I just followed the fixes pointed out removing  all occurence of **X86_64** bits from the build scripts compile_ios_protobuf.sh & compile_ios_tensorflow.sh and then running build_all_ios.sh
works great on device.
